<p><span class="anchor" id="p59"></span>فَلَو جهلاها أَو أَحدهمَا لم يَصح<a href="#p59" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p60"></span>وَكَذَا غَيرهمَا<a href="#p60" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p61"></span>أَي معرفَة عَدْلَيْنِ غير الْعَاقِدين<a href="#p61" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
